Description: A complete Uno card game engine built with R6 for mutable game
    state, S4 for validated configuration, and S3 for game results and
    leaderboards. Includes an Rcpp-powered simulation engine for comparing
    bot strategies and a Shiny dashboard for interactive play, simulation,
    and leaderboards.
